name: FlokiTer
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en:
What is the project about?
FlokiTer AI is a great revolution in combining blockchain technology with Artificial Intelligence to support CEOs build up their stunning NFT images.
$FAI is a Memecoin driven by the community. The FlokiTer Token was created as a result of Elon Musk's recent promotion of his beloved dog Floki to the position of NEW CEO of Twitter.
We are a group of AI developers with NFT digital experiences and backgrounds, our team is specializing in digital 3D, Visual effects, and crypto marketing.

What makes your project unique?
The FlokiTer AI team will help project owners, artists, and normal users to create stunning NFT images and collections.
AI Art generation is usually a laborious process that requires technical expertise, we make that process simple and intuitive.


History of your project.
Whitepaper and Website Development Done
Contract Creation Done
Contact Audit Done
KYC Done
FlokiTer Launch and Marketing Done
NFT Staking Dapp Under Processing

What’s next for your project?
CEX Listings
NFT Staking Dapp Launch
NFT Minting
Mobile App Development

What can your token be used for?
Trading
3D NFT Utility Usage
Usage of the Mobile App to use AI developed system for creating 3D NFTs
